Package: r2vcftools
Title: An R interface for vcftools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Nate", "Pope", email = "nspope@utexas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a wrapper for some filtering/query functionality
    from vcftools (which it requires!), for the truly lazy, like myself, who don't
    like to switch between bash and R to do visualization.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2),
    LEA
Imports:
    LEA,
    methods
License: GPL 3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: 
    awk,
    perl,
    vcftools
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Collate:
    'vcflink.R'
    'conversion.R'
    'utils.R'
    'filter.R'
    'fst.R'
    'query.R'
    'r2vcftools.R'
